parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding doors can cause them to open or close unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or trapping occupants inside the vehicle.
symptoms: The doors may not latch or unlock properly
or open/close unexpectedly while driving. The door alarm may sound
and the doors may not respond to manual or automatic operation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door latches can cause the doors to open or close unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or trapping occupants inside the vehicle.
symptoms: The doors may not latch or unlock properly
or open/close unexpectedly while driving. The door alarm may sound
and the doors may not respond to manual or automatic operation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding door latch can cause the door to open or close unexpectedly while driving, leading to accidents or injuries. It can also prevent passengers from exiting the vehicle in an emergency.
symptoms: The door will not latch or unlatch
the door opens or closes unexpectedly
the door is difficult to open or close
the door will not stay shut
the interior lights and buzzer stay on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door lock can prevent passengers from exiting the vehicle in an emergency, especially if the internal child safety lock is also engaged.
symptoms: The child safety lock will not disengage
the passenger is unable to unlock the door from the inside
